com.metreeca.back.stardog

Class Stardog

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.metreeca.back.sparql.Graph
      • com.metreeca.back.stardog.Stardog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    public final class Stardog
extends Graph
    Stardog graph store.

    Manages task execution on an Stardog repository.

    Warning / the isolation level is set to IsolationLevels.READ_COMMITTED, unless explicitly overridden during tray configuration, like:

    
 tray.set(Graph.Factory, () -> new Stardog(…).isolation(IsolationLevels.NONE);

    Note that this limitation seems to be specific of the RDF4J interface, as at the repository configuration level available transaction options are SNAPSHOT and SERIALIZABLE…
